PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1988-2604 increasing the amount of a loan made by the Export Development Corporation to the China National Chemical Construction Corporation in order to finance the purchase of certain equipment and services needed for the construction of a chemical plant at Jiujiang China, which are to be supplied by SNC Services Ltd.

precis:
Amendment to Order in Council P.C. 1988-2604 increasing the amount of a
loan made by the Export Development Corporation to the China National
Chemical Construction Corporation in order to finance the purchase of
certain equipment and services needed for the construction of a chemical
plant at Jiujiang China, which are to be supplied by SNC Services Ltd.
